2 of our Beauty Ambassadors created their very OWN Liquid Matte Lipstick!! 

Soooo excited to finally reveal something that is so special to me and the team. In 2019, we collaborated with two of our amazing Beauty Ambassadors in the UK and brought them to Dubai to create their very own #LiquidMatte lipstick. Sana (from @theofficialselfridges) and Bilkis (from @harrodsbeauty) work their butts off to give people the products of their dreams, and we couldn't be more thankful for everything they do. My loves, it's been such an honor working with you both on creating your perfect shade and I'm sooooooo excited for the world to finally see them!!

💄'QUEEN OF SHEBA' by Bilkis (from @harrodsbeauty)– A royal pinky nude 💋

💄'GIRL ON FIRE' by Sana (from @theofficialselfridges) - A hot & toasted sexy red (what I’m currently wearing)💋 

I am OBSESSED with the shades they made & cant wait for you all to try them!! Officially dropped only on @harrodsbeauty & @theofficialselfridges
